{"tid":1675710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣可唔可以幫手搞個大型聲援維族 西藏人既集會","createTime":"2019-10-26T05:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:11:20.000Z","uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37a58d8ede3125d0cf63ca9600495ec4311281c9","tid":1675710,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"之前大家有搞加泰集會<br />\n嚟緊睇到有人想搞智利集會<br />\n但係其實admin想講<br />\n我哋一定要搞一個支持新疆維族人嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48878300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48878300&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=af2840a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48878300&h=66cba7bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48878300</a><br />\n我講緊係每一個有人性嘅人都要支持佢哋<br />\nAdmjn們懇求各單位合作幫手搞一個聲援維族人嘅集會出嚟<br />\n(順便Connect muslim<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />種族滅絕正在進行中"},{"pid":"7312bbf406c1e7a6552729e495e64677369f1fb8","tid":1675710,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d82deefaad1c5adbb3999b1d593dd874515ab1","tid":1675710,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7312bbf406c1e7a6552729e495e64677369f1fb8","tid":1675710,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你好撚鬼"},{"pid":"31292fd12b7e776175bcd7e2270ab180297e2952","tid":1675710,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99fe5d43ce92c6e464694a21d11775023f765bf","tid":1675710,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"Admin喺英國曾經識得一位維族媽媽<br />\n佢喊住同我分享以下嘅經歷：<br />\n佢老公返去新疆探病咗嘅父母<br />\n然後就消失左<br />\n當佢帶着兩位10幾歲嘅女去搵老公嘅時候（佢俾相我睇過，兩個都好靚女....<br />\n就係入境之後俾仆街中共捉咗去集中營<br />\n跟住發生嘅事大家都應該係新聞見過<br />\n最過分嘅<br />\n班仆街喺媽媽面前輪姦佢兩個女<br />\n媽媽有反應就即刻一棍打落去<br />\n最尾佢兩個女唔知用咩條件令媽媽放出去(媽媽推測係佢哋自願服侍班狗官以換取媽媽安全）<br />\n媽媽有善心人士帶佢逃亡<br />\n從此以後就音訊全無<br />\n<br />\n我聽完真係喊到收唔到聲<br />\n每次諗返起都仲覺得好撚嬲好撚傷心...."},{"pid":"71725c12b1fce44c32a286c94f0247206075aac7","tid":1675710,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"790bd6928f79b9d6b6a3fbed6b65c0fc9d1ac09f","tid":1675710,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"dd66d8fab72010df888ce79ddff77b20711333b0","tid":1675710,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705dc8b5a3462b091d7470c956d0b33bb4cf6158","tid":1675710,"uid":280612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"我撐加泰集會，但亦都同意其實撐新疆重要過加泰好多"},{"pid":"18354b5795df920ab92dfa15f8f0bd8d5869f003","tid":1675710,"uid":312833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37a58d8ede3125d0cf63ca9600495ec4311281c9","tid":1675710,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"之前大家有搞加泰集會<br />\n嚟緊睇到有人想搞智利集會<br />\n但係其實admin想講<br />\n我哋一定要搞一個支持新疆維族人嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48878300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48878300&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN5gFNMR